<p>For the <code>Background</code> step, we <em>now</em> know we could create a matching
definition in <code>FeatureContext</code> and easily use Mink's session object
to actually go to that URL. But earlier when we ran this scenario,
it worked... so there must already be something tie'ing Behat and
Mink together.</p>
<p>Let's see what's happening.</p>
<h2 id="free-behat-steps">Free Behat Steps <a class="headerlink" href="behat-loves-mink#free-behat-steps" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
