                <i class="fa fa-spinner fa-spin js-icon-loading"></i>
            </td>
            <td class="gap-line">
                                                    ... lines 7 - 11
                            </td>
            </tr>

        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>
</p>
<p>Since we don't need JavaScript, and now we should be able to run our search feature. Perfect!</p>

    
